WHEREAS, while her passing leaves a profound void, her legacy endures through
her family, her contributions to public service, and the countless lives she touched with her
kindness, wisdom, and generosity.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby express its deepest condolences to the family and friends of Kathleen "Kathy"
Sessums and does honor and celebrate her remarkable life and enduring legacy of service,
love, and leadership.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
family of Kathleen "Kathy" Sessums as an expression of the Senate's sympathy and respect.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
